Source: jwltief
Section: games
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Christoph Korn <christoph.korn@getdeb.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9),
               libsdl1.2debian [i386],
               libsdl-image1.2 [i386],
               libsdl-mixer1.2 [i386],
               libsdl-ttf2.0-0 [i386]
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: http://games.aleva.com.br/jwltief

Package: jwltief
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         jwltief-bin (= ${source:Version})
Description: Play a thief and collect jewels
 Jwltef is a game where you control a
 thief with the mouse and aim to collect
 as many jewels as possible, dodging
 moving enemies.

Package: jwltief-bin
Architecture: i386
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         jwltief-data (= ${source:Version})
Description: Play a thief and collect jewels (binary package)
 Jwltef is a game where you control a
 thief with the mouse and aim to collect
 as many jewels as possible, dodging
 moving enemies.
 .
 (This package contains the executable).

